      "weather": "FINE",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLACK MYTH WAVE (2) has been out of the placings last two but prior to that posted a scintillating 29.41 win over 520m at this track. Hot win three back and looks the one to beat here. INTREPID EAGLE (3) hit the ground running and was prominent to the turn but faded out of it when 6th at this track in NG company. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with two wins from three starts. Shapes as one to consider. QUEEN ERA (1) turned in a big run last time despite being beaten, finishing second in a Grade 5 behind Nangar Charm in a flying 29.70 and clocking a new PB. In form and looks a leading player again. O'KEEFE (7) placed last start and is in the mix again.",
